Library.neuralnetwork

Class NeuralNetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • Library.neuralnetwork.NeuralNetwork

  • public class NeuralNetwork
extends Object
    This is the main class that connects all other classes, this is what the user instantiates in the main class and calls whatever training method is needed.
    Author:
    Sulman and Abubakar

      • createHiddenLayer

        public org.nd4j.linalg.api.ndarray.INDArray createHiddenLayer(int numOfInputNeurons,
                                                              int numOfHiddenNeurons)
        This method creates the connection matrix between the input layer and hidden layer.
        Parameters:
        inputlayerSize - - size of the input layer which will be used as the first dimension of the array.
        numOfHiddenNeurons - - size of the hidden layer that will be used for the second dimension of the array.
        Returns:
        - returns a INDArray containing random weights varying from -0.5 to 0.5.

      • createOutputLayer

        public org.nd4j.linalg.api.ndarray.INDArray createOutputLayer(int numOfHiddenNeurons,
                                                              int numOfOutputNeurons)
        This method creates the connection matrix between the hidden layer and output layer.
        Parameters:
        numOfHiddenNeurons - - size of the hidden layer which is used as the first dimension of the weight array.
        numOfOutputNeurons - - size of the output layer which is used as the second dimension of the weight array.
        Returns:
        - returns a INDArray containing random weights varying from -0.5 to 0.5.
